Document: PhysicsBody3D
Path: godot/classes/class_physicsbody3d.rst
Summary: This section details the properties of the PhysicsBody3D class, specifically focusing on axis locking for linear and angular movement.

Properties
* axis_lock_angular_x (bool): Locks the body's rotation around the X axis. Default: false.
* axis_lock_angular_y (bool): Locks the body's rotation around the Y axis. Default: false.
* axis_lock_angular_z (bool): Locks the body's rotation around the Z axis. Default: false.
* axis_lock_linear_x (bool): Locks the body's movement along the X axis. Default: false.
* axis_lock_linear_y (bool): Locks the body's movement along the Y axis. Default: false.
* axis_lock_linear_z (bool): Locks the body's movement along the Z axis. Default: false.
